screen_name: Ok. After SEVEN DAYS! AN ENTIRE WEEK OF WAITING! I am officially COVID-19 positive and finally have an idea of when I can leave isolation. Days like today make me wish I was famous/important and could have gotten this information in a matter of hours. https://t.co/jEIO7knQQU

It has been SIX (6) days since I got tested for COVID-19 and have yet to hear results back. I am going crazy waiting for instructions on what to do next. My 14-day self-quarantine was supposed to end today, I've now been isolated for 6. Results change everything.
